                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        < p class="text-sm opacity-80 mt-2" > Acceleration = (Final Velocity - Initial Velocity) / Time</p >
