                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                < p class="text-sm text-green-700 mt-2" > <strong>Quick Trick: </strong> To estimate yearly salary, double your hourly rate and add three zeros. (e.g., $25/hr → $50 → $50,000).</p>
